query:
INSERT INTO price_history
                (timestamp, chf, usd, eur, gbp, btc)
                VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT(timestamp) DO UPDATE SET
            chf=excluded.chf,
            usd=excluded.usd,
            eur=excluded.eur,
            gbp=excluded.gbp,
            btc=excluded.btc;
